	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_36517148"><p><div class="quote"><p>Bitcoin has absolutely no use other than as a fiat currency.</p></div><p>Bitcoins are not a fiat currency.  A fiat currency, as should be obvious from its name, has its value set by fiat (decree).  No one is decreeing that bitcoins have value, any more than anyone decrees that monopoly money has value.  It's fashionable for libertarians to use the word 'fiat' to mean 'worthless', but the two words are not interchangeable.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_36517148">
<span class="ind"></span><a class="btn link" href="//yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=2256616&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;cid=36514922" onclick="return D2.selectParent(36514922)">Parent</a> 	<a href="#" class="comment_share_toggle btn link">Share</a>
	<div class="comment_share sharethis-0 hide"><span class="au"></span>
